          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ff6b6b' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='13'>KEY FINDING</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#f2f2f7' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>M0→M1 drop: −15.7pp average</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#f2f2f7' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>The steepest retention loss occurs</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#f2f2f7' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>in the first 30 days.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#f2f2f7' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>Accounts that don&apos;t activate in</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#f2f2f7' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>Month 1 rarely recover.</run>
          </formatted-text>
